---
// Professional intro section: the bridge between design intent and buildable construction
---

<section class="intro">
  <div class="container intro__inner">
    <div class="intro__text">
      <p class="label label-accent reveal">专业定位</p>
      <h2 class="intro__heading reveal reveal-delay-1">
        连接<em>方案设计</em>与<br>现场施工的专业桥梁
      </h2>
      <div class="intro__body reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <p>我是一名专注于景观施工图设计的专业人员，自 2017 年起从事这一领域至今。我的核心工作是将景观方案效果图、设计意图和概念方案，转化为清晰、准确、施工团队可直接执行的施工图纸。</p>
        <p>我的工作不只是"画图"——它需要同时理解设计语言和施工逻辑，在两者之间找到平衡点：既保留原设计的效果与意图，又确保图纸在实际施工条件下具有可操作性。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="intro__stats reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-item__number">2017</span>
        <span class="stat-item__label">年开始从业</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-item__number">6+</span>
        <span class="stat-item__label">代表项目经验</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-item__number">多省</span>
        <span class="stat-item__label">项目落地经验</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.intro {
  padding-block: var(--space-section);
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border-bottom: 1px solid oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.07);
}

.intro__inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
  gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 8rem);
  align-items: center;
}

.intro__text {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.intro__heading {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-cn);
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  line-height: 1.35;
  color: var(--color-ink);
}

.intro__heading em {
  font-style: normal;
  color: var(--color-accent);
}

.intro__body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-4);
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  max-width: 560px;
}

.intro__stats {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  border: 1px solid oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.08);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.stat-item {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-2);
  padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-10);
}

.stat-divider {
  height: 1px;
  background: oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.08);
}

.stat-item__number {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-en);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 1.5rem + 2vw, 3.5rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--color-accent);
  line-height: 1;
}

.stat-item__label {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-cn);
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}

@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .intro__inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .intro__stats {
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: space-around;
  }
  .stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: auto;
  }
}
</style>
